title: A 25-Year-Old Sample Contributes the Complete Genome Sequence of Avian Coronavirus Vaccine Strain ArkDPI, Reisolated from Commercial Broilers in the United States
body: The complete genome sequence of the GA/1359/1994 isolate of the ArkDPI-like strain has been deposited in GenBank under the accession number MN566147. The raw data were deposited under SRA accession number SRR10742607, BioSample number SAMN13020879, and BioProject number PRJNA556282.
